ge":3.334},{"width":1950,"height":2926,"file_path":"/gzyCJAnKlRsHFy2DDV0aRzZ9ZGx.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","vote_average":0},{"width":1488,"height":2124,"file_path":"/1AxrxAxWP5LyDJ8V1uEN7LmUfEC.jpg","iso_639_1":"ja","vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/pyPUP9OOID2I3ZRfDlSrSavxLrJ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/8LQbej9aBSvpXU9m1E8DWEC9rOH.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/twq1UYjHcuHCuC63Nv7C3JcjA8G.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/bwzX5zCtPOOeEQg5hzeh6rY8abJ.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/jLG8kvJnifJBK6S7g1vYiS9eURj.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/fd0FJuWcq4d6S1s7aZ1sRrYVcyg.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T05:19:44.68+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Thunderbolt Fantasy 生死一劍","runtime":75,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://thunderboltfantasy.com.tw/SwordLifeDeath","overview":"《Thunderbolt Fantasy：生死一劍》由日本動漫界神級大師虛淵玄擔任原案‧腳本‧總監修，與台灣布袋戲的龍頭霹靂國際多媒體共同打造，雙方堪稱奇蹟般攜手合作所帶來的台日共同影像作品，本作是改編自小說《Thunderbolt Fantasy 東離劍遊紀 外傳》中所收錄的〈殺無生篇〉，加上「虛淵玄」親自執筆之「殤不患」新作短篇，將兩者影像化的作品。  【殺無生篇】  「殺無生篇」為改編自《Thunderbolt Fantasy 東離劍遊紀 外傳》〈殺無生篇〉的影像作品，為《Thunderbolt Fantasy 東離劍遊紀》的前傳故事。以凜雪鴉性命為目標、執拗追殺著他的殺無生，過去與凜雪鴉的一段因緣將在故事中揭明。擔任凜雪鴉保鑣的殺無生，為了與自己的過去訣別，在凜雪鴉的勸進下參加了較量劍技的「劍聖會」。然而，一場應該較量劍技的大會上，卻出現了弓箭名手參戰，局勢動向透著隱約不安……  【殤不患篇】:  「殤不患篇」為虛淵玄親自執筆撰寫的《Thunderbolt Fantasy 東離劍遊紀》後傳故事。在與蔑天骸、玄鬼宗、魔神等一戰過後，東離再度恢復和平。與丹翡、捲殘雲他們告別，繼續著旅程的殤不患，來到了一家冷清的客棧酒館。在那裡，他遇上了一個男人……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Thunderbolt Fantasy: The Sword of Life and Death","runtime":75,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"A theatrical spinoff of the 'Thunderbolt Fantasy' television series which explores the backstory of Shā Wú Shēng, the Screaming Phoenix Killer, and bridges the events of the first and second seasons."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.thunderboltfantasy.com/gaiden","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"썬더볼트 판타지: 생사일검","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"[살무생 편]  [Thunderbolt Fantasy 동리검유기]의 전일담  늠설아의 목숨을 노려 집요하게 그를 쫗고있던 살무생과 늠설아와의 과거의 인연이 밝혀진다  늠설아의 호위역을 맡고있던 살무생은 과거와 결별하기위해 늠설아의 추천으로 검기를 겨루는 대회 [검성회]에 출장하게 된다.  하지만 검기를 겨루는 대외이었을 터인데, 활의 명수가 참전하는등, 무언가 불온한 움직임이...  [상불환 편]  [Thunderbolt Fantasy 동리검유기]의 후일담  멸천해와 현귀종, 마신과의 싸움의 뒤 평화를 되찾은 동리  단비와 권산운과 해어져 여행을 계속하는 상불환은 어떤 낡은 역참의 술집에 들르게 되고 거기서 어떤 남자를 만나게 되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Thunderbolt Fantasy: The Sword of Life and Death","runtime":0,"tagline":"La espada de la vida y la muerte","homepage":"","overview":"El episodio de Setsu Mu Syou tiene lugar un año antes de la primera temporada de Thunderbolt Fantasy . El asesino profesional Setsu Mu Syou ha sido contratado como guardaespaldas personal del notorio ladrón Lin Setsu A. Setsu Mu Syou expresa sus pensamientos de un cambio en el estilo de vida de Lin Setsu A mientras viajan por la tierra, ya que no desea estar a la altura de su nombre siniestro que se le dio como resultado de las desgracias que rodearon su nacimiento.  El Episodio de Syou Fu Kan , por otro lado, es un segmento corto que tiene lugar entre las dos primeras temporadas de Thunderbolt Fantasy . Syou Fu Kan llega a una pequeña posada en una ciudad, donde conoce a un hombre que repentinamente proclama que es Syou Fu Kan, y que él solo terminó el reinado de terror del Genkishuu sobre Dong-Li matando a Betsu Ten Gai. . El verdadero Syou Fu Kan decide escuchar la historia del hombre, un recuento exagerado e incorrecto de los eventos de la primera temporada."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"东离剑游纪：生死一剑","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"《生死一剑》是由虚渊玄原案，黄强华总执导、郑保品执导的《东离剑游纪》系列布袋戏电影。该影片分为“杀无生篇”和“殇不患篇”两部分。“杀无生篇”改编自江波光则原作的轻小说《东离剑游纪外传》其中的“杀无生篇”，是《东离剑游纪》的前传故事。“殇不患篇”是虚渊玄亲自执笔撰写的《东离剑游纪》后传故事。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Thunderbolt Fantasy : The Sword of Life and Death","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sha Wu Sheng, l'assassin connu sous le nom de Screaming Phoenix Killer, portait une inimitié mortelle contre l'Enigmatic Gale, un maître voleur. Mais ces deux hommes n'étaient pas toujours en désaccord - en fait, Wu Sheng était autrefois employé par Enigmatic Gale, et il considérait même son employeur comme un sauveur potentiel. Il a fallu un tournoi malheureux pour détruire le lien entre eux, dont les circonstances seront enfin révélées dans ce spécial Thunderbolt Fantasy ! Après cela, l'histoire se tourne vers Shang Bu Huan, révélant où son chemin l'a mené à la suite de son voyage à Demon Spine Mountain."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ซีรีส์ภาคแยกของซีรีส์ทางโทรทัศน์เรื่อง 'Thunderbolt Fantasy' ซึ่งสำรวจเรื่องราวเบื้องหลังของ Shā Wú Shēng หรือฆาตกรนกฟีนิกซ์ผู้กรีดร้อง และเชื่อมโยงเหตุการณ์ในซีซั่นแรกและซีซั่นที่สองเข้าด้วยกัน"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sha Wu Sheng, de huurmoordenaar die bekend staat als de Screaming Phoenix Killer, koesterde een dodelijke vijandschap tegen de Enigmatic Gale, een meesterdief. Maar deze twee mannen waren het niet altijd oneens - in feite was Wu Sheng ooit in dienst van Enigmatic Gale, en hij zag zijn werkgever zelfs als een potentiële redder. Er was een ongelukkig toernooi voor nodig om de band tussen hen te vernietigen, waarvan de omstandigheden eindelijk zullen worden onthuld in deze Thunderbolt Fantasy-special! Daarna gaat het verhaal over Shang Bu Huan en onthult waar zijn pad hem bracht als gevolg van zijn reis naar Demon Spine Mountain."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":11972,"adult":false,"title":"The Little World of Don Camillo","video":false,"overview":"In a village of the Po valley where the earth is hard and life miserly, the priest and the communist mayor are always fighting to be the head of the community. If in secret, they admired and liked each other, politics still divided them as it is dividing the country. And when the mayor wants his \"People's House\"; the priest wants his \"Garden City\" for the poor. Division exist between the richest and the poorest, the pious and the atheists and even between lovers. But if the people are hard as the country, they are good in the bottom of there heart.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8557,"vote_count":300,"poster_path":"/bDbzuBgsgZ5VVljMHNni3gJK9Qx.jpg","release_date":"1952-03-28","vote_average":7.583,"backdrop_path":"/p1rU5RalhYCTDpasCFTwhKp795J.jpg","original_title":"Don Camillo","original_language":"it"},{"id":245891,"adult":false,"title":"John Wick","video":false,"overview":"Ex-hitman John Wick comes out of retirement to track down the gangsters that took everything from him.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.2495,"vote_count":20483,"poster_path":"/wXqWR7dHncNRbxoEGybEy7QTe9h.jpg","release_date":"2014-10-22","vote_average":7.454,"backdrop_path":"/ff2ti5DkA9UYLzyqhQfI2kZqEuh.jpg","original_title":"John Wick","original_language":"en"},{"id":177677,"adult":false,"title":"Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation","video":false,"overview":"Ethan and team take on their most impossible mission yet—eradicating 'The Syndicate', an International and highly-skilled rogue organization committed to destroying the IMF.","genre_ids":[28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7364,"vote_count":9545,"poster_path":"/fRJLXQBHK2wyznK5yZbO7vmsuVK.jpg","release_date":"2015-07-28","vote_average":7.221,"backdrop_path":"/vYIUN5rrCncHFY8WvcuXQlM4hk5.jpg","original_title":"Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.5844,"vote_count":14038,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.8777,"vote_count":1120,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.704,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":22.369,"vote_count":11378,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":565770,"adult":false,"title":"Blue Beetle","video":false,"overview":"Recent college grad Jaime Reyes returns home full of aspirations for his future, only to find that home is not quite as he left it. As he searches to find his purpose in the world, fate intervenes when Jaime unexpectedly finds himself in possession of an ancient relic of alien biotechnology: the Scarab.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.1521,"vote_count":3023,"poster_path":"/mXLOHHc1Zeuwsl4xYKjKh2280oL.jpg","release_date":"2023-08-16","vote_average":6.647,"backdrop_path":"/3H9NA1KWEQN0ItL3Wl3SFZYP6yV.jpg","original_title":"Blue Beetle","original_language":"en"},{"id":718930,"adult":false,"title":"Bullet Train","video":false,"overview":"Unlucky assassin Ladybug is determined to do his job peacefully after one too many gigs gone off the rails. Fate, however, may have other plans, as Ladybug's latest mission puts him on a collision course with lethal adversaries from around the globe—all with connected, yet conflicting, objectives—on the world's fastest train.","genre_ids":[28,35,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.4624,"vote_count":7280,"poster_path":"/j8szC8OgrejDQjjMKSVXyaAjw3V.jpg","release_date":"2022-08-03","vote_average":7.413,"backdrop_path":"/y2Ca1neKke2mGPMaHzlCNDVZqsK.jpg","original_title":"Bullet Train","original_language":"en"},{"id":76341,"adult":false,"title":"Mad Max: Fury Road","video":false,"overview":"An apocalyptic story set in the furthest reaches of our planet, in a stark desert landscape where humanity is broken, and most everyone is crazed fighting for the necessities of life. Within this world exist two rebels on the run who just might be able to restore order.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.674,"vote_count":23774,"poster_path":"/hA2ple9q4qnwxp3hKVNhroipsir.jpg","release_date":"2015-05-13","vote_average":7.629,"backdrop_path":"/l0eIS009XtEO80aC6zjM3o3AkEl.jpg","original_title":"Mad Max: Fury Road","original_language":"en"},{"id":680,"adult":false,"title":"Pulp Fiction","video":false,"overview":"A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.","genre_ids":[53,80,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":24.5798,"vote_count":29724,"poster_path":"/vQWk5YBFWF4bZaofAbv0tShwBvQ.jpg","release_date":"1994-09-10","vote_average":8.486,"backdrop_path":"/96hiUXEuYsu4tcnvlaY8tEMFM0m.jpg","original_title":"Pulp Fiction","original_language":"en"},{"id":150540,"adult":false,"title":"Inside Out","video":false,"overview":"When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.","genre_ids":[16,10751,12,18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":15.6045,"vote_count":23182,"poster_path":"/2H1TmgdfNtsKlU9jKdeNyYL5y8T.jpg","release_date":"2015-06-17","vote_average":7.909,"backdrop_path":"/jJKZaTBNenlFclQyjrnvzkRmvWE.jpg","original_title":"Inside Out","original_language":"en"},{"id":9502,"adult":false,"title":"Kung Fu Panda","video":false,"overview":"Chosen by prophecy but doubted by all, Po is an unlikely Dragon Warrior—a clumsy panda thrust into the world of kung fu as a deadly enemy threatens the Valley of Peace. Guided by Master Shifu and the Furious Five, Po must embrace who he is to unlock the power that no scroll can teach.","genre_ids":[16,10751,35,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.4344,"vote_count":12404,"poster_path":"/wWt4JYXTg5Wr3xBW2phBrMKgp3x.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-04","vote_average":7.314,"backdrop_path":"/qdthf9WrRDSaIkGVQGhhJ9pz1hn.jpg","original_title":"Kung Fu Panda","original_language":"en"},{"id":93456,"adult":false,"title":"Despicable Me 2","video":false,"overview":"Gru is recruited by the Anti-Villain League to help deal with a powerful new super criminal.","genre_ids":[16,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.0618,"vote_count":11848,"poster_path":"/5Fh4NdoEnCjCK9wLjdJ9DJNFl2b.jpg","release_date":"2013-06-26","vote_average":6.942,"backdrop_path":"/fOipappvgVtUbbHOtmCkHzcwJjC.jpg","original_title":"Despicable Me 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":389,"adult":false,"title":"12 Angry Men","video":false,"overview":"The defense and the prosecution have rested and the jury is filing into the jury room to decide if a young Spanish-American is guilty or innocent of murdering his father. What begins as an open and shut case soon becomes a mini-drama of each of the jurors' prejudices and preconceptions about the trial, the accused, and each other.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":12.3315,"vote_count":9760,"poster_path":"/ow3wq89wM8qd5X7hWKxiRfsFf9C.jpg","release_date":"1957-04-10","vote_average":8.556,"backdrop_path":"/w4bTBXcqXc2TUyS5Fc4h67uWbPn.jpg","original_title":"12 Angry Men","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.7749,"vote_count":25448,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":400928,"adult":false,"title":"Gifted","video":false,"overview":"Frank, a single man raising his child prodigy niece Mary, is drawn into a custody battle with his mother.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.3129,"vote_count":5852,"poster_path":"/9Ts7Vc4wLlpI9oox9mkVUE1tBHy.jpg","release_date":"2017-04-07","vote_average":7.999,"backdrop_path":"/aH63TQfTFgAT8tYZs0CjDsqfMo2.jpg","original_title":"Gifted","original_language":"en"},{"id":24428,"adult":false,"title":"The Avengers","video":false,"overview":"When an unexpected enemy emerges and threatens global safety and security, Nick Fury, director of the international peacekeeping agency known as S.H.I.E.L.D., finds himself in need of a team to pull the world back from the brink of disaster. Spanning the globe, a daring recruitment effort begins!","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":54.3753,"vote_count":36054,"poster_path":"/RYMX2wcKCBAr24UyPD7xwmjaTn.jpg","release_date":"2012-04-25","vote_average":7.949,"backdrop_path":"/pGFQCp12a8andfPlpnmXz44IIvY.jpg","original_title":"The Avengers","original_language":"en"},{"id":118340,"adult":false,"title":"Guardians of the Galaxy","video":false,"overview":"Light years from Earth, 26 years after being abducted, Peter Quill finds himself the prime target of a manhunt after discovering an orb wanted by Ronan the Accuser.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.5358,"vote_count":29349,"poster_path":"/r7vmZjiyZw9rpJMQJdXpjgiCOk9.jpg","release_date":"2014-07-30","vote_average":7.905,"backdrop_path":"/vmBSlRZYKfNdaDZ7wGkrSNbmdMI.jpg","original_title":"Guardians of the Galaxy","original_language":"en"},{"id":577922,"adult":false,"title":"Tenet","video":false,"overview":"Armed with only one word - Tenet - and fighting for the survival of the entire world, the Protagonist journeys through a twilight world of international espionage on a mission that will unfold in something beyond real time.","genre_ids":[28,53,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.4016,"vote_count":10863,"poster_path":"/aCIFMriQh8rvhxpN1IWGgvH0Tlg.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-22","vote_average":7.175,"backdrop_path":"/yY76zq9XSuJ4nWyPDuwkdV7Wt0c.jpg","original_title":"Tenet","original_language":"en"},{"id":209112,"adult":false,"title":"Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice","video":false,"overview":"Fearing the actions of a god-like Super Hero left unchecked, Gotham City’s own formidable, forceful vigilante takes on Metropolis’s most revered, modern-day savior, while the world wrestles with what sort of hero it really needs. And with Batman and Superman at war with one another, a new threat quickly arises, putting mankind in greater danger than it’s ever known before.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.5902,"vote_count":18762,"poster_path":"/5UsK3grJvtQrtzEgqNlDljJW96w.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-23","vote_average":5.989,"backdrop_path":"/mwuP3Ah8b7SKnmSCk8EaQw7jrEq.jpg","original_title":"Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":278615,"adult":false,"title":"Who Said Meow?","video":false,"overview":"After hearing someone's \"meow\" for the first time in his life, baby puppy goes in search of the unknown beast and meets various inhabitants of the house and yard. On children's curiosity and the first acquaintance with the world.","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.1142,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/3f3wj6vCI3pcjSAmjQWY6OaMQMu.jpg","release_date":"1962-01-01","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Кто сказал мяу?","original_language":"ru"},{"id":32393,"adult":false,"title":"The Puppetoon Movie","video":false,"overview":"Animated characters introduce a compilation of George Pal replacement animation Puppetoon short films from the 1930s and 1940s.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":0.5276,"vote_count":9,"poster_path":"/lVBVeAjsdLDU29jMqDRcb7EMqOE.jpg","release_date":"1987-06-12","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/xEy95wB4alftfwVqBd3KFbFiGuB.jpg","original_title":"The Puppetoon Movie","original_language":"en"},{"id":728414,"adult":false,"title":"Sisters","video":false,"overview":"Two sisters squabble and fight with each other over the course of their lives.","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.7433,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/dtKpSd2D43YFmTXdK4HzPT87n1S.jpg","release_date":"1974-01-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Õed","original_language":"et"},{"id":728421,"adult":false,"title":"Jonn","video":false,"overview":"Three selfish fishermen are in danger because of their great envy. And although fate has mercy on them, the men do not learn from it, but everything repeats itself. Estonian/Soviet animation short from 1966.","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.6267,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/DOunDAvtpc4QZodgvegptj76Yr.jpg","release_date":"1966-06-20","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":"/9MlVnqR2K19fX3zOmzXhKt1w2jq.jpg","original_title":"Jonn","original_language":"et"},{"id":123957,"adult":false,"title":"Bobby Yeah","video":false,"overview":"Bobby Yeah is a petty thug who lightens his miserable existence by brawling and stealing stuff. One day, he steals the favourite pet of some very dangerous individuals, and finds himself in deep trouble. He really should learn, but he just can't help it.","genre_ids":[16,27],"popularity":1.0759,"vote_count":38,"poster_path":"/A9gKUDeuVQU1frU465IeCCahHiv.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-04","vote_average":7.092,"backdrop_path":"/9O8X66iDoEEows2khSnzgDrfuGp.jpg","original_title":"Bobby Yeah","original_language":"en"},{"id":572043,"adult":false,"title":"Pizza Passionata","video":false,"overview":"The loneliest man in the suburbs opens his door to a stranger and gets caught up in the merry-go-round of love.","genre_ids":[16,10749],"popularity":0.4216,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/9ExxjrfIbnBnNKSEA4pAdR08hvO.jpg","release_date":"2001-09-13","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Pizza Passionata","original_language":"fi"},{"id":146928,"adult":false,"title":"Tulips Shall Grow","video":false,"overview":"In this Puppetoon animated short film (an Academy Award Best Short Subject, Cartoons nominee), a young Dutch couple find their idyllic countryside being overrun by unfeeling, unthinking mechanical men and machines that lay waste to everything in their path. In 1997 this film, deemed \"culturally, historically, or aesthetically significant,\" was selected for preservation in the United States National Film Registry.","genre_ids":[16,10752],"popularity":0.2308,"vote_count":31,"poster_path":"/3JvFXR1LHRGZqX5ZpDTcXx2CgLf.jpg","release_date":"1942-01-26","vote_average":6.774,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Tulips Shall Grow","original_language":"en"},{"id":211507,"adult":false,"title":"Tubby the Tuba","video":false,"overview":"In this Puppetoon animated short film (an Academy Award Best Short Subject, Cartoons nominee), Tubby the Tuba is disappointed that his sound limits what he's permitted to do in an orchestra of self-playing instruments that, unlike him, get to play pretty melodies. A chance meeting with a bullfrog changes everything.","genre_ids":[16,10751,10402],"popularity":0.2805,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/tkN0dCjqKKsUqLYXWQcAUvc0WXB.jpg","release_date":"1947-07-11","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Tubby the Tuba","original_language":"en"},{"id":236556,"adult":false,"title":"Hoola Boola","video":false,"overview":"Jim Dandy lands on a tropical island and falls in love with a beautiful maiden. A Puppetoon animated short film.","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.5856,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/fo50x6OKkfhyuTHWOAXezdJaErX.jpg","release_date":"1941-06-27","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Hoola Boola","original_language":"en"},{"id":802675,"adult":false,"title":"Chaisson: Rise of the Zerad","video":false,"overview":"Driven from his homeland and faced with the genocide of his people, an inexperienced Elvish prince must forge an unlikely alliance with a tribe of Wolfmen to save his people from the bloodthirsty Zerad.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,14],"popularity":0.0974,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/pb1f6NiQ8nQYgBciFbnzQSandFF.jpg","release_date":"2010-05-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/E0OHa14C1wG4KSQ3UnML3Fr0eq.jpg","original_title":"Chaisson: Rise of the Zerad","original_language":"en"},{"id":613221,"adult":false,"title":"Daughter","video":false,"overview":"A young girl buries in her soul a memory of a painful moment, when as a child she brought home an injured bird and her father burdened by his own weight of worries didn’t notice her feelings and longing for understanding.  The girl took her father’s reaction as indifference and closed herself in her inner world longing for her father’s love and its manifestations. Since that moment she and her dad continued to grow apart, and as an adult she is no longer able to accept his endearments. The father suffers from guilt and searches for a way back to his daughter, trying to revive their lost relationship.","genre_ids":[16,18],"popularity":0.5232,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/jnjBY3FywWNlZqc8QOBf6CTJJKD.jpg","release_date":"2019-06-29","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/bHvjsEFY4kDKmhqNx3MNlwO6xLQ.jpg","original_title":"Dcera","original_language":"cs"},{"id":846867,"adult":false,"title":"Mad God","video":false,"overview":"A figure known as \"The Assassin\" descends from the heavens into a nightmarish pit full of monsters, titans, and cruelty.","genre_ids":[16,14,27,878],"popularity":1.8956,"vote_count":530,"poster_path":"/105stT9GkiENXiYqvWYKoAuHKQL.jpg","release_date":"2021-09-17","vote_average":6.811,"backdrop_path":"/eMDQdKeoWTrCm2wEs7I7OD3bTQl.jpg","original_title":"Mad God","original_language":"en"},{"id":260023,"adult":false,"title":"The Sleeping Beauty","video":false,"overview":"Centuries ago in the past, the witch, who doesn't like Beauty, puts her to sleep, then flies throughout the castle spreading sleep powder, placing all into slumber. Eventually we flash forward to present time: A young hepcat in a convertible tries awakening Sleeping Beauty, and everyone in the castle, with some Big Band music. Will it work? A Puppetoon animated short film.","genre_ids":[16,10751],"popularity":0.2797,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1935-01-01","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Sleeping Beauty","original_language":"en"},{"id":253764,"adult":false,"title":"Philips Cavalcade","video":false,"overview":"In this Puppetoon animated short film, a variety of music styles are heard as, in various locations, characters dance or sing.","genre_ids":[16],"popularity":0.2599,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1934-02-02","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Philips Cavalcade","original_language":"en"},{"id":260471,"adult":false,"title":"Together in the Weather","video":false,"overview":"In this Puppetoon animated short film, Judy, an enticing blonde, lives across the way from Punchy and uses all her feminine wiles to try to snare him.","genre_ids":[16,35],"popularity":0.1161,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1946-03-22","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Together in the Weather","original_language":"en"},{"id":642586,"adult":false,"title":"Thunderbolt Fantasy: Bewitching Melody of the West","video":false,"overview":"Làng Wū Yáo is a boy born with a supernatural singing voice. Secluded in the snowy mountains, he is put through severe training by his blind mother. Her wish is for her son's voice to be unrivaled, so that it will be heard by the imperial court. But the intense training results in a tragic accident, where she dies.  Left an orphan as a result, Làng wanders the land. His voice is used as a tool by the wicked and greedy, with his heart being ground down in the process.  Eventually his strange singing catches the ear of the princess of Xī Yōu, and Làng is elevated to the stage his mother had dreamt of. But what awaits him is a life or death battle performance against other musicians for the amusement of the members of the court.","genre_ids":[28,18,14,12,16],"popularity":2.2321,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/4OwAY0SpHwkx70qAWU5adAlLvmq.jpg","release_date":"2019-10-25","vote_average":5.5,"backdrop_path":"/gOjLDFzdAUkuZ2NMNTYQkxhXSTr.jpg","original_title":"Thunderbolt Fantasy 西幽玹歌","original_language":"ja"},{"id":441999,"adult":false,"title":"Birthday Night","video":false,"overview":"The Night had her birthday, and gave a party to which she invited Dima, a little boy so afraid of the dark that he could never sleep when the light was out.","genre_ids":[16,14,10751],"popularity":0.1019,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/hNlme5t6vs2tcP5tVyOU7LtasaL.jpg","release_date":"1980-02-16","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Ночь рождения","original_language":"ru"},{"id":236695,"adult":false,"title":"The Little Broadcast","video":false,"overview":"The Great Maestro gets to conduct more than he can compose himself to. A Puppetoon animated short film.","genre_ids":[10402,16],"popularity":0.1303,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/iHgrCuK6TTwzUCfrWiEWSzDd4BB.jpg","release_date":"1943-09-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"The Little Broadcast","original_language":"en"},{"id":253976,"adult":false,"title":"Jasper in a Jam","video":false,"overview":"In this entertaining Puppetoon animated short film, a young boy, Jasper, gets trapped inside a pawnshop at midnight. All the musical instruments come to life and play jazz. A whooping wooden Indian chief self-animates as well, and goes on the warpath.","genre_ids":[16,10402],"popularity":0.1395,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"1946-10-18","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Jasper in a Jam","original_language":"en"},{"id":295876,"adult":false,"title":"How to Become a Grown-Up","video":false,"overview":"A little slacker doesn't appreciate his childhood and wants to face with adult problems as quickly as possible.","genre_ids":[16,10751],"popularity":0.1177,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/e2csn44AfsPKbj3CBzSFAH6fSRv.jpg","release_date":"1967-10-01","vote_a